JEAN ONE?

231
00:10:45,353 --> 00:10:46,312
I GUESS...

232
00:10:46,312 --> 00:10:48,356
HARD TO SAY, REALLY...

233
00:10:49,691 --> 00:10:51,901
HEY, HOW LONG ARE YOU
GUYS GOING TO KEEP GOOFING OFF?

234
00:10:51,901 --> 00:10:53,778
GET BACK TO YOUR STATIONS AND
START WORKING!

235
00:10:54,529 --> 00:10:56,281
Allelujah:
IS OUR MEETING OVER?

236
00:10:56,281 --> 00:10:58,658
Setsuna:
YEAH. BUT THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE
I HAVE TO DO.

237
00:10:58,658 --> 00:10:59,868
Tieria:
SOMETHING ELSE?

238
00:10:59,868 --> 00:11:01,452
I'LL BE ESCORTING
MARINA ISMAIL

239
00:11:01,452 --> 00:11:03,288
BACK TO THE COUNTRY OF
AZADISTAN.

240
00:11:03,288 --> 00:11:05,164
SO, YOU'RE SAYING...

241
00:11:05,164 --> 00:11:06,875
ARE YOU SURE
THIS IS WHAT YOU WANT?

242
00:11:06,875 --> 00:11:09,544
I'M TRULY SORRY FOR ALL
THE TROUBLE I'M CAUSING.

243
00:11:09,544 --> 00:11:10,628
HMM...

244
00:11:10,628 --> 00:11:12,630
WELL, YOU CAN'T GO BACK
IN A GUNDAM.

245
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:14,674
ON THE OFF CHANCE
YOU'RE DISCOVERED...

246
00:11:14,674 --> 00:11:17,176
YOU COULD BRING FURTHER HARM
DOWN UPON AZADISTAN.

247
00:11:18,177 --> 00:11:20,388
THEN LET ME HAVE
THE USE OF THIS CRAFT.

248
00:11:20,388 --> 00:11:21,764
YOU CAN USE
THE GUNDAM.

249
00:11:21,764 --> 00:11:23,516
THAT'LL WORK.

250
00:11:23,516 --> 00:11:26,227
AND DON'T FEEL LIKE YOU HAVE
TO COME BACK, EITHER.

251
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:28,438
THAT'S ABSURD.

252
00:11:28,438 --> 00:11:31,399
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU
OVER THESE PAST FOUR YEARS?

253
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:33,484
FOR YOU TO ACTUALLY
TELL A JOKE IS...

254
00:11:33,484 --> 00:11:35,028
I WAS SERIOUS
BACK THERE.

255
00:11:35,028 --> 00:11:35,820
WHAT?

256
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:37,071
(Chuckles)

257
00:11:37,071 --> 00:11:39,657
NOW, THAT WAS A JOKE.

258
00:11:44,495 --> 00:11:46,247
CELESTIAL BEING AND
KATHARON...

259
00:11:46,247 --> 00:11:48,583
BOTH OF THEM ARE
GROUPS THAT CAUSE FIGHTING!

260
00:11:48,583 --> 00:11:50,710
I CAN'T STAY
IN A PLACE LIKE THIS!

261
00:11:55,048 --> 00:11:56,591
HEY, WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING THERE?

262
00:11:56,591 --> 00:11:58,426
NOTHING!
I WAS JUST...

263
00:11:58,426 --> 00:12:00,970
OH, YOU'RE WITH CELESTIAL BEING,
AREN'T YOU?

264
00:12:00,970 --> 00:12:02,764
HUH?

265
00:12:02,764 --> 00:12:05,975
I'VE GOT COMRADES
IN TOWN I NEED TO TALK TO.

266
00:12:05,975 --> 00:12:08,686
NEAREST TOWN IS A LONG WAY FROM
HERE, TAKE A VEHICLE!

267
00:12:08,686 --> 00:12:10,104
HUH?

268
00:12:10,855 --> 00:12:11,940
THANK YOU!

269
00:12:15,068 --> 00:12:17,362
HAVE YOU SEEN PRINCESS MARINA
WANDERING AROUND?

270
00:12:17,362 --> 00:12:18,821
I JUST SAW HER WITH SOME
CELESTIAL BEING PEOPLE

271
00:12:18,821 --> 00:12:20,114
A FEW
MOMENTS AGO.

272
00:12:20,114 --> 00:12:21,991
SHE WAS WITH THEM?

273
00:12:21,991 --> 00:12:23,826
Announcer:
THE GUNDAMS ARE RETURNING TO
THEIR MOTHER SHIP!

274
00:12:23,826 --> 00:12:24,577
OPEN THE HATCH!

275
00:12:24,577 --> 00:12:25,578
(Gasps)

276
00:12:27,997 --> 00:12:29,540
COULD...
COULD SHE BE...?

277
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:31,292
WE HAVE TO
STOP THEM FROM TAKING OFF!

278
00:12:31,292 --> 00:12:32,669
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE NOW.

279
00:12:36,130 --> 00:12:37,507
MARINA...

280
00:12:37,507 --> 00:12:50,436
♪

281
00:12:50,436 --> 00:12:54,107
I WONDER IF I CAN MAKE IT ACROSS
THE WHOLE DESERT IN THIS.

282
00:12:54,107 --> 00:12:55,108
HUH?

283
00:12:58,695 --> 00:13:00,655
(Stammering)
THE FEDERATION!

284
00:13:09,914 --> 00:13:12,417
WHY ARE YOU CROSSING THE DESERT
WITH SO LITTLE EQUIPMENT?

285
00:13:12,417 --> 00:13:13,376
(Panting)

286
00:13:15,712 --> 00:13:17,714
WE GOT A HIT
ON HIS BIOMETRICS.

287
00:13:17,714 --> 00:13:19,590
OUR FRIEND HERE IS A
MEMBER OF KATHARON!

288
00:13:19,590 --> 00:13:20,925
I'M NOT!

289
00:13:20,925 --> 00:13:22,385
I SWEAR I'VE NEVER BEEN
A MEMBER OF THAT GROUP!

290
00:13:22,385 --> 00:13:23,803
ENOUGH
OF YOUR LYING!

291
00:13:24,387 --> 00:13:26,305
STOP, THERE'S NO NEED
TO ROUGH HIM UP!

292
00:13:26,305 --> 00:13:27,890
WHA‐‐
COLONEL!

293
00:13:27,890 --> 00:13:29,017
Sergei:
GET OUT.

294
00:13:29,017 --> 00:13:30,601
I WANT TO HEAR
HIS STORY.

295
00:13:30,601 --> 00:13:31,853
(Growling)

296
00:13:34,355 --> 00:13:36,482
YOU'RE NOT REALLY A SOLDIER,
ARE YOU, BOY?

297
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:37,692
HMM?

298
00:13:37,692 --> 00:13:40,111
I'M AN OLD SOLDIER,
I CAN TELL THESE THINGS.

299
00:13:40,111 --> 00:13:42,947
YOU DON'T HAVE THE EYES OF
SOMEONE WHO'S SEEN COMBAT.

300
00:13:42,947 --> 00:13:46,075
IN OTHER WORDS, YOU'RE CLEARLY
NOT A MEMBER OF KATHARON.

301
00:13:46,075 --> 00:13:48,536
SO, WHAT IN THE WORLD
HAVE YOU BEEN UP TO?

302
00:13:48,536 --> 00:13:50,204
HUH.

303
00:13:50,204 --> 00:13:54,167
YOU'VE BEEN TRAVELING WITH
CELESTIAL BEING, HAVEN'T YOU?

304
00:13:54,167 --> 00:13:55,084
(Gasps)

305
00:13:55,084 --> 00:13:56,711
IT'S PLAUSIBLE.

306
00:13:56,711 --> 00:13:59,422
ACCORDING TO THE DATA,
UNTIL A FEW WEEKS AGO,

307
00:13:59,422 --> 00:14:02,258
YOU WERE WORKING ON
COLONY DEVELOPMENT AT PROUD,

308
00:14:02,258 --> 00:14:04,427
WHERE THE GUNDAMS FIRST
RE‐APPEARED.

309
00:14:04,427 --> 00:14:06,387
AND NOW YOU'RE IN THE SAME
REGION WHERE THERE WAS

310
00:14:06,387 --> 00:14:08,973
A BATTLE YESTERDAY
WITH THE GUNDAMS.

311
00:14:08,973 --> 00:14:10,058
IT'S NOTHING.

312
00:14:10,058 --> 00:14:11,893
IT'S JUST
SIMPLE REASONING.

313
00:14:14,062 --> 00:14:16,606
I'M...

314
00:14:16,606 --> 00:14:18,900
...NOT WITH KATHARON OR
CELESTIAL BEING.

315
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:20,359
I BELIEVE YOU.

316
00:14:20,359 --> 00:14:22,987
I JUST WANT TO HEAR
YOUR SIDE OF THE STORY, BOY.

317
00:14:22,987 --> 00:14:24,947
I WON'T
USE IT AGAINST YOU.

318
00:14:25,615 --> 00:14:27,366
(Gasps)

319
00:14:27,366 --> 00:14:30,119
Saji:
CAN YOU GET ME
CLEARED OF ALL SUSPICIONS?

320
00:14:30,119 --> 00:14:31,245
Sergei:
I'LL DO WHAT I CAN.

321
00:14:32,288 --> 00:14:34,082
Zinin:
CAPTAIN BARACK ZININ, SIR.

322
00:14:34,082 --> 00:14:36,125
WITH ALL FIVE MEMBERS
OF SPACE TEAM FOUR.

323
00:14:36,125 --> 00:14:39,337
PRESENT
AND REPORTING FOR DUTY.

324
00:14:39,337 --> 00:14:40,338
GOOD WORK, TEAM.

325
00:14:40,338 --> 00:14:42,298
Goodman:
WHAT?
IS THIS TRUE?

326
00:14:42,298 --> 00:14:44,300
I'LL ISSUE THE ORDERS
IMMEDIATELY.

327
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:45,885
IF WE LEFT IT
TO THAT NAÏVE WOMAN,

328
00:14:45,885 --> 00:14:48,054
SHE'D BE SURE TO
MESS THIS UP.

329
00:14:48,054 --> 00:14:49,597
EXCELLENT NEWS,
COMMANDER.

330
00:14:49,597 --> 00:14:52,725
WE'VE DISCOVERED
KATHARON'S MILITARY BASE,

331
00:14:52,725 --> 00:14:55,311
AND THERE'S A VERY GOOD CHANCE
THE GUNDAMS ARE THERE TOO.

332
00:14:55,311 --> 00:14:56,979
WE NEED TO ATTEND
TO THIS IMMEDIATELY.

333
00:14:56,979 --> 00:14:58,439
SIR!

334
00:14:58,439 --> 00:15:00,691
COMMANDER, PERMISSION FOR OUR
TEAM TO SORTIE AS WELL.

335
00:15:00,691 --> 00:15:02,068
NO NEED
TO PUSH YOURSELVES.

336
00:15:02,068 --> 00:15:03,861
TAKE IT EASY
FOR NOW.

337
00:15:03,861 --> 00:15:05,196
(Frustrated sigh)

338
00:15:05,196 --> 00:15:07,615
THE GUNDAMS ARE OUT THERE,
AND YET...

339
00:15:07,615 --> 00:15:09,951
Kati:
WH... WHAT KIND
OF AN ORDER IS THIS?

340
00:15:09,951 --> 00:15:13,121
WE'RE EXPECTED TO MAKE USE OF
AUTOMATONS IN KILL MODE?

341
00:15:13,121 --> 00:15:14,497
THIS IS CRAZY!

342
00:15:14,497 --> 00:15:16,249
THIS OPERATION IS BARBARIC!

343
00:15:16,249 --> 00:15:17,625
COLONEL.

344
00:15:17,625 --> 00:15:20,211
AN ORDER FROM THAT HIGH UP HAS
TO BE STRICTLY FOLLOWED.

345
00:15:20,211 --> 00:15:22,046
YOU'RE TELLING ME YOU DON'T
THINK THERE'S SOMETHING WRONG

346
00:15:22,046 --> 00:15:23,589
ABOUT THE DETAILS
OF THIS OPERATION?

347
00:15:23,589 --> 00:15:25,758
NOW WHY WOULD I
THINK SUCH A THING?

348
00:15:25,758 --> 00:15:28,136
WE'RE FIGHTING THE
ANTI‐GOVERNMENT FORCES.

349
00:15:28,136 --> 00:15:31,597
THERE'S NO NEED TO SHOW THEM
ANY MERCY, NOW IS THERE?

350
00:15:31,597 --> 00:15:32,974
(Frustrated sigh)

351
00:15:39,897 --> 00:15:42,441
AN OPERATION
LIKE THIS ONE...

352
00:15:42,441 --> 00:15:44,360
NOW, I FINALLY UNDERSTAND
WHY THE COLONEL

353
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:47,029
WAS SO FIRMLY
OPPOSED TO MY REASSIGNMENT.

354
00:15:47,029 --> 00:15:48,948
YOU'VE GOT HIM WRONG,
LIEUTENANT.

355
00:15:48,948 --> 00:15:50,616
COLONEL SMIRNOV
IS THE KIND OF MAN

356
00:15:50,616 --> 00:15:52,410
WHO WOULD ABANDON HIS OWN
FLESH AND BLOOD

357
00:15:52,410 --> 00:15:53,953
TO MAKE SURE HE
FULFILLED HIS DUTY.

358
00:15:53,953 --> 00:15:55,913
HIS FLESH AND BLOOD?

359
00:15:55,913 --> 00:15:58,499
YES, THAT MAN ALLOWED
MY MOTHER TO DIE.

360
00:15:58,499 --> 00:15:59,458
(Gasps)

361
00:16:00,501 --> 00:16:02,086
(Uneasy sigh)

362
00:16:04,672 --> 00:16:06,174
Liu Mei:
SO...

363
00:16:06,174 --> 00:16:11,637
THE A‐LAWS KNOW
WHERE THE DISSIDENTS ARE.

364
00:16:11,637 --> 00:16:13,097
I UNDERSTAND.

365
00:16:13,097 --> 00:16:15,641
I'LL LET TIERIA
AND THE OTHERS KNOW.

366
00:16:19,729 --> 00:16:20,605
Sergei:
YOU IDIOT!

367
00:16:20,605 --> 00:16:22,231
(Slam)

368
00:16:22,231 --> 00:16:25,026
WHO TOLD YOU TO
REPORT THIS INFO TO A‐LAWS?

369
00:16:25,026 --> 00:16:26,986
BUT SIR, IT'S OUR DUTY
TO REPORT THESE THINGS!

370
00:16:26,986 --> 00:16:29,197
THAT IS MY DECISION TO MAKE,
SOLDIER!

371
00:16:29,989 --> 00:16:30,781
HUH?

372
00:16:30,781 --> 00:16:32,200
MR. CROSSROAD.

373
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,410
COME WITH ME, YOU HAVE TO GET
OUT OF HERE RIGHT NOW.

374
00:16:34,410 --> 00:16:35,870
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

375
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:38,247
I'M AFRAID YOUR PRESENCE HERE
WAS LEAKED TO THE A‐LAWS.

376
00:16:38,247 --> 00:16:41,250
THEY'RE A GROUP THAT OPERATES
ABOVE THE LAW.

377
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:43,502
I DON'T HAVE ENOUGH AUTHORITY TO
PROTECT YOU WHEN THEY SHOW UP.

378
00:16:43,502 --> 00:16:44,587
BUT THAT'S‐‐

379
00:16:44,587 --> 00:16:45,880
YOU HAVE TO HURRY!

380
00:16:48,466 --> 00:16:51,552
SOMEBODY LEAKED THE FACT
THAT I WAS THERE...

381
00:16:51,552 --> 00:16:53,012
SO, DOES THAT MEAN THAT‐‐

382
00:16:53,012 --> 00:16:54,597
HUH?

383
00:16:54,597 --> 00:16:55,681
THAT COLOR!

384
00:16:57,433 --> 00:16:59,894
Feldt:
EMERGENCY CODED MESSAGE
FROM WANG LIU MEI.

385
00:16:59,894 --> 00:17:01,771
APPARENTLY AN A‐LAWS
MOBILE SUIT TEAM

386
00:17:01,771 --> 00:17:03,856
IS HEADED DIRECTLY
FOR THE KATHARON BASE.

387
00:17:03,856 --> 00:17:05,191
WHAT SHOULD WE DO NOW?

388
00:17:05,191 --> 00:17:06,776
WE'RE GOING
TO GO HELP THEM.

389
00:17:06,776 --> 00:17:08,569
ANTI‐SATELLITE
OPTICAL CAMOUFLAGE,

390
00:17:08,569 --> 00:17:10,154
EMERGENCY ASCENT!

391
00:17:10,154 --> 00:17:12,031
TELL THE GUNDAMS
TO GET READY TO LAUNCH.

392
00:17:12,031 --> 00:17:13,574
THAT'S A ROGER!

393
00:17:13,574 --> 00:17:15,910
Feldt:
PTOLEMY BEGINNING
EMERGENCY ASCENT.

394
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:18,871
0043 UNTIL SURFACING.

395
00:17:18,871 --> 00:17:20,539
THE A‐LAWS
FOUND THEIR BASE...?

396
00:17:20,539 --> 00:17:23,376
BUT THERE ARE A LOT OF INNOCENT
CHILDREN WITH THEM, AS WELL.

397
00:17:23,376 --> 00:17:24,710
HURRY IT UP!

398
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:26,671
DAMN IT, WE'RE RUNNING OUT OF
TIME, HURRY IT UP!

399
00:17:30,591 --> 00:17:31,842
(Siren wails)

400
00:17:31,842 --> 00:17:33,970
IT'S AN A‐LAWS
MOBILE SUIT TEAM!

401
00:17:33,970 --> 00:17:35,888
WAIT, ARE THEY GOING TO
ATTACK THIS PLACE?

402
00:17:35,888 --> 00:17:37,139
HOW MANY OF THEM
ARE COMING?

403
00:17:37,139 --> 00:17:39,225
BUT HOW DID THEY
FIND OUT ABOUT OUR BASE?

404
00:17:39,225 --> 00:17:41,185
IT COULDN'T HAVE BEEN FROM
CELESTIAL BEING, COULD IT?

405
00:17:41,185 --> 00:17:42,853
QUICKLY, GET THE CHILDREN
TO THE SHELTER!

406
00:17:42,853 --> 00:17:43,854
O‐OKAY!

407
00:17:43,854 --> 00:17:46,023
KLAUS, LET'S GO OUT
AND FIGHT!

408
00:17:46,023 --> 00:17:48,067
NO, WE'RE STILL
TOO BADLY OUTMATCHED!

409
00:17:48,067 --> 00:17:49,402
WE'LL STRENGTHEN
OUR DEFENSES

410
00:17:49,402 --> 00:17:51,487
AND WAIT FOR CELESTIAL BEING
TO COME TO OUR AID!

411
00:17:51,487 --> 00:17:52,697
ARE THEY EVEN
GOING TO SHOW UP?

412
00:17:52,697 --> 00:17:53,948
I BELIEVE IN THEM!

413
00:17:53,948 --> 00:17:54,949
(Startled yelling)

414
00:17:54,949 --> 00:17:56,158
THEY'RE BOMBING US?

415
00:17:56,158 --> 00:17:58,452
(Panicked murmuring)

416
00:17:58,452 --> 00:18:00,621
(People screaming)

417
00:18:02,623 --> 00:18:04,250
Andrei:
I HAVE VISUAL CONFIRMATION

418
00:18:04,250 --> 00:18:06,168
OF A STRUCTURE THAT
LOOKS LIKE AN ENEMY BASE.

419
00:18:06,168 --> 00:18:06,961
HUH?

420
00:18:09,130 --> 00:18:11,465
(Rapid blasting)

421
00:18:11,465 --> 00:18:13,009
Andrei:
ENEMY MOBILE SUITS!

422
00:18:16,178 --> 00:18:18,014
THEY'RE STILL USING OUTDATED
MOBILE SUITS.

423
00:18:19,724 --> 00:18:20,808
(Frustrated sigh)

424
00:18:26,105 --> 00:18:28,441
Commander #3:
COMMENCE MOPPING‐UP
OPERATION OF ENEMY BASE.

425
00:18:28,441 --> 00:18:29,859
RELEASE AUTOMATONS.

426
00:18:29,859 --> 00:18:30,818
Pilot #30A:
ROGER.

427
00:18:30,818 --> 00:18:31,902
THEY WOULDN'T...

428
00:18:34,488 --> 00:18:36,699
Pilot #30A:
RELEASING AUTOMATONS.

429
00:18:36,699 --> 00:18:37,825
NO, WAIT A MINUTE!

430
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:41,495
(Coughing)

431
00:18:42,121 --> 00:18:43,581
WAIT...
THOSE ARE...

432
00:18:48,377 --> 00:18:50,838
(Mechanical marching)

433
00:18:50,838 --> 00:18:52,798
THEY'RE MILITARY
AUTOMATONS!

434
00:18:52,798 --> 00:18:54,634
EVERYONE,
FALL BACK, NOW!

435
00:18:54,634 --> 00:18:56,052
FALL BACK!

436
00:18:58,137 --> 00:18:59,221
(Blast)

437
00:19:01,599 --> 00:19:02,808
DAMN, WE'RE TOO LATE!

438
00:19:02,808 --> 00:19:04,518
WHAT ABOUT
THE KATHARON PEOPLE?

439
00:19:04,518 --> 00:19:06,103
Lyle:
I'LL LEAVE THIS
TO YOU GUYS!

440
00:19:07,730 --> 00:19:09,899
GET A MOVE ON,
GUNDAM!

441
00:19:13,486 --> 00:19:15,988
Commander #3:
PERIES! INTERCEPT
THAT FIRST GUNDAM!

442
00:19:15,988 --> 00:19:17,156
Peries:
ROGER!

443
00:19:19,533 --> 00:19:21,952
(Blasting rapidly)

444
00:19:24,789 --> 00:19:26,540
HE'S GOT
SOME MOVES!

445
00:19:26,540 --> 00:19:28,626
Commander #3:
ALL MACHINES
AFTER THE OTHER GUNDAMS!

446
00:19:28,626 --> 00:19:30,378
Bushido:
I'LL BE SITTING
THIS ONE OUT.

447
00:19:30,378 --> 00:19:31,962
Commander #3:
MR. BUSHIDO?
BUT WHY?

448
00:19:31,962 --> 00:19:33,673
I DON'T FEEL LIKE IT!

449
00:19:35,883 --> 00:19:37,259
(Gasping)
THIS IS...

450
00:19:42,723 --> 00:19:44,225
IS THIS...

451
00:19:44,225 --> 00:19:47,311
IS THIS SOMETHING
HUMAN BEINGS WOULD DO?

452
00:19:49,313 --> 00:19:50,856
(Gasping)

453
00:19:50,856 --> 00:19:52,733
Allelujah:
MASS MURDER
WITH AUTOMATED WEAPONS.

454
00:19:56,320 --> 00:19:58,447
(Pilot screaming)

455
00:19:58,447 --> 00:20:01,659
YOU THINK JUST BECAUSE YOU AVOID
PULLING THE TRIGGER YOURSELF

456
00:20:01,659 --> 00:20:04,412
YOU WON'T FEEL ANY OF THE
GUILT FROM COMMITTING THE CRIME?

457
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,875
READY DOUBLE BAZOOKA...

458
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:11,085
BURST MODE!

459
00:20:16,715 --> 00:20:18,509
Commander #3:
WE'VE ACHIEVED OUR
INITIAL OBJECTIVE!

460
00:20:18,509 --> 00:20:20,428
TIME TO WITHDRAW!

461
00:20:21,053 --> 00:20:22,430
(Rapid machine‐gun fire)

462
00:20:24,723 --> 00:20:25,766
(Gasps)

463
00:20:25,766 --> 00:20:27,560
(Tense sigh)

464
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:32,648
Lyle:
I'LL NEVER FORGIVE YOU!

465
00:20:32,648 --> 00:20:34,233
I'LL NEVER FORGIVE YOU
FOR THIS, A‐LAWS!

466
00:20:36,902 --> 00:20:38,904
DON'T YOU DARE RUN!

467
00:20:38,904 --> 00:20:41,449
DON'T YOU DARE
RUN AWAY FROM ME, A‐LAWS!

468
00:20:49,748 --> 00:20:50,833
Feldt:
IT'S HORRIBLE...

469
00:20:50,833 --> 00:20:53,502
(Trembling sigh)

470
00:20:54,462 --> 00:20:55,838
Allelujah:
SO THIS IS...

471
00:20:55,838 --> 00:20:57,173
A‐LAWS...

472
00:20:57,173 --> 00:20:58,382
Tieria:
THAT'S RIGHT.

473
00:20:58,382 --> 00:21:00,301
THIS IS THE ENEMY
WE ARE SWORN TO DEFEAT!

474
00:21:06,307 --> 00:21:09,018
