THE HAPPINESS

477
00:21:14,857 --> 00:21:16,400
THAT NORMAL PEOPLE
TAKE FOR GRANTED.

478
00:21:20,237 --> 00:21:22,865
COLONEL, COULD THIS BE
MY PUNISHMENT...

479
00:21:22,865 --> 00:21:23,574
FOR WANTING THAT?

480
00:21:31,749 --> 00:21:33,751
(Grieving sighs)

481
00:21:36,837 --> 00:21:39,298
ALL BECAUSE...

482
00:21:39,298 --> 00:21:41,383
ALL THIS BECAUSE
I TALKED TO THEM...

483
00:21:45,554 --> 00:21:46,722
(Sobbing)

484
00:21:46,722 --> 00:21:47,890
THIS CAN'T BE...

485
00:21:49,099 --> 00:21:50,434
THIS CAN'T BE...

486
00:21:50,434 --> 00:21:52,686
(Sobbing)

487
00:21:52,686 --> 00:21:56,482
THIS CAN'T BE HAPPENING!

