493
00:23:27,281 --> 00:23:29,325
Setsuna:
WE'LL BE IN AZADISTAN
SHORTLY.

494
00:23:29,325 --> 00:23:30,701
I'M RETURNING
AFTER ALL.

495
00:23:30,701 --> 00:23:32,202
THAT'S RIGHT.

496
00:23:32,202 --> 00:23:33,621
BACK TO YOUR COUNTRY.

497
00:23:33,621 --> 00:23:34,622
HMM.

498
00:23:40,919 --> 00:23:43,047
(Gasping)
AZADISTAN IS...

499
00:23:43,047 --> 00:23:45,049
EVERYTHING'S BURNING...

500
00:23:45,049 --> 00:23:47,384
Marina:
BUT WHY IS AZADISTAN...

501
00:23:47,384 --> 00:23:49,136
WHY?

502
00:23:49,136 --> 00:23:50,846
THE SCALE...

503
00:23:50,846 --> 00:23:53,057
NOT TERRORISTS.

504
00:23:53,057 --> 00:23:54,642
(Gasping)

505
00:23:54,642 --> 00:23:55,851
IT'S...

506
00:23:55,851 --> 00:23:57,811
A GUNDAM!

507
00:23:57,811 --> 00:24:00,439
AND THAT COLOR!

508
00:24:00,439 --> 00:24:01,857
IS IT HIM?

509
00:24:02,733 --> 00:24:04,526
Al‐Saachez:
THAT'S RIGHT!

510
00:24:04,526 --> 00:24:06,111
YOU GUESSED RIGHT, PUNK!

